temprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text=
-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color=
: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> come aroun=
d</a> to <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24393206.=
255798/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDEt=
MjYvd2lsbC13YWxsc3RyZWV0YmV0cy1mYWNlLXNlYy1zY3J1dGlueS1hZnRlci1nYW1lc3RvcC1=
yYWxseQ/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB0a26f2ed" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; b=
order-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style:=
 solid; background-color: #ccc;"> the view</a> that many small-cap pump-and=
-dump schemes look like the first type of scam but are really the third. So=
me stock shill sends out an email newsletter saying =E2=80=9Cbuy Amalgamate=
d Widgets because they are about to announce a breakthrough Covid cure,=E2=
=80=9D and then Amalgamated Widgets stock goes up rapidly and then down rap=
idly again, and from the outside you can look at it and say =E2=80=9Cah, pe=
ople were tricked into thinking that Amalgamated Widgets had a Covid cure,=
=E2=80=9D but the shill=E2=80=99s newsletter is titled Stock Shill Weekly a=
nd the only subscribers are people who want to play pump-and-dumps and nobo=
dy believes it, it=E2=80=99s just an excuse for everyone to play a gambling=
 game where the loser is whoever gets out last.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin=
: 16px 0;">There is no reason at all to sympathize with victims of the thir=
d sort of scam; often they don=E2=80=99t sympathize with themselves. They d=
on=E2=80=99t perceive themselves as victims, because they aren=E2=80=99t; t=
hey think they played a game of chance and lost. They got their money=E2=80=
=99s worth, in expectation; they had their fun and it cost them a reasonabl=
e amount of their gambling money.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Obviously=
 in practice these things can blur into each other; if you are playing the =
fun gambling game (type 3) you might also be hoping to get an edge (type 2)=
