or: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bo=
rder-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #=
ccc;">its IPO prospectus</a>, and =E2=80=9Cit=E2=80=99s never been easier o=
r more delightful to build a portfolio and invest for the long term.=E2=80=
=9D If=C2=A0<em>they=C2=A0</em>thought constant trading was good they would=
 have said something else. =E2=80=9CA lot of our customers prefer to YOLO w=
eekly call options and make a lot of money doing it,=E2=80=9D or whatever. =
Robinhood=E2=80=99s major=C2=A0innovation was building an app, and an econo=
mic model, that made it easy and pleasant for regular people to trade a lot=
. Perhaps that=E2=80=99s good! It does seem controversial.</p><h2 style=3D"=
